The components of Xtensible Library

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExtensibleLinearOpMode.EventWatcher
    The Event Watcher for the Linear OpMode execution system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExtensibleGamepad
    The extensible Gamepad, based on Gamepad.
    ExtensibleGamepad.Dpad
    An representation of a gamepad's D-Pad control
    ExtensibleGamepad.Joystick
    The Joystick for use in ExtensibleGamepad.
    ExtensibleHardwareMap
    The new version of the hardware map that provides a safer use for the hardware map.
    ExtensibleLinearOpMode
    An extensible version of a linear OpMode, designed for higher levels of synchronisation as well as better access to the underlying loop.
    ExtensibleLoopManager
    This is the configuration manager for how ExtensibleOpMode loops.
    ExtensibleOpMode
    The main Xtensible OpMode, any desirable OpMode that this library presents has at one point devired from this class.

    ImmutableHardwareMap

    NetworkedOpMode
    The Networking components of the library; inherit this class to use the Networking components in an OpMode
    PerformanceTuner
    A serializable class that describes key info in how a loop performs in operation

    RobotContext  
    RobotLogger

    Watchdog
